        "Number of passengers carried Fiscal Year Passengers (millions) Source 2022/23 143.1 [2] 2023/24 220.3 [2] 2024/25 242.9 [2] Further proposals Main article: Crossrail § Further proposals A new station has been proposed to serve London City Airport, and extensions have been put forward to Ebbsfleet in the south east, Milton Keynes in the north west, Staines in the south west, and Southend Airport in the east.",
